reviewText: Not as expected with entire dvd an interview with a leading ufo researcher

Pope is one of very few UFO experts that have first hand experience with government conspiracy. He is a highly reputable source. This is a neat & tidy DVD, entertaining yet not overstuffed with fluff.
I have watched a number of ufo videos and I must say this is one of a few that I consider on a new level. More modern and on the tip than most.

I really enjoyed this video, especially the parts about capturing your own ufo footage. It's finally becoming obvious that the government can't keep this information hidden any longer. A must for ufo buffs.
